Gene Expression Analysis Platform

Instructions

1. Setup web app:
cd webapp
pip3 install --upgrade pip
pip install -r requirements.txt

2. Set FLASK_APP environmental variable (required):
export FLASK_APP=app

3. Run the web app
flask run
# or run the web app on a specific port (replace xxxx with port#):
flask run -h 0.0.0.0 -p xxxx
